casebody.data:
No. —, Original.

The Texas-Cherokees and Associate Bands v. State of Texas. Motion for leave to file bill of complaint submitted November 14, 1921. Decided November 21, 1921. Mr. William Sulzer for complainant. Per Curiam.

The motion for leave to. file an original bill of complaint in this case is denied upon authority of Cherokee Nation v. Georgia, 5 Pet. 1.
